#5 REAL-TIME USE CASES OF BLOCKCHAIN TECHNOLOGY
1.Digital Payments & Money Transfer
Simple idea: Send money fast without banks.
	â€¢	Blockchain allows people to send money directly to each other.
	â€¢	No bank or middleman is needed.
	â€¢	Money reaches in minutes, even across countries.
