	â€¢	Bitcoin, USDT, UPI-like payments on blockchain
Why useful?
âœ” Fast
âœ” Low cost
âœ” Works 24/7
2ï¸. Banking & Finance (DeFi)
Simple idea: Banking without banks.
	â€¢	People can save, lend, or borrow money using apps.
	â€¢	Smart contracts do the work automatically.
	â€¢	Anyone with internet can use it.
Example:
Aave, MakerDAO
Why useful?
âœ” No paperwork
âœ” No bank control
âœ” Open to everyone
3ï¸.Supply Chain (Tracking Products)
Simple idea: Track where a product comes from.
	â€¢	Every step of a product is recorded on blockchain.
	â€¢	Data cannot be changed or faked.
Example:
	â€¢	Walmart tracking food, De Beers tracking diamonds
Why useful?
âœ” Stops fake products
âœ” Builds trust
âœ” Easy tracking
4ï¸. Voting & Government Records
